When formatting JavaScript the indent of right parenthesis (that is placed on different line) is too large.
This is expected to be

``` javascript
function (
    arg1,
    arg2
) {
    if (
        arg1
        && arg2
    ) {
        //...
    }
}
```

but actually is

``` javascript
function (
    arg1,
    arg2
    ) {
    if (
        arg1
        && arg2
        ) {
        //...
    }
}
```

My user keybindings.json is like this:
    [
    {
    "key": "ctrl+/",
    "command": "editor.action.commentLine && cursorDown",
    "when": "editorTextFocus" 
    }
    ]
But it doesn't work.
